  "Times New Roman",ExpressionUUID->"bd725b91-6c4e-41c5-a63f-f72435719f81"],

Cell["\<\
Remember, this gives us the coefficients of the basis we chose to start with:\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9068197721847315`*^9, 3.90681979139797*^9}},
 FontFamily->
  "Times New Roman",ExpressionUUID->"542db367-c9fe-4b2e-b86c-a755b88d04f9"],

Cell[TextData[{
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"{", 
    RowBox[{"1", ",", "x", ",", 
